Package: chemometrics4all
Title: R Binding for the chemometrics4all C ABI (libc4a)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "chemometrics4all", family = "authors",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "chemometrics4all@example.org"))
Author: chemometrics4all authors [aut, cre]
Maintainer: chemometrics4all authors <chemometrics4all@example.org>
Description: Thin R binding for the chemometrics4all C ABI (libc4a). Exposes
    a tier-1 .Call layer that dispatches into the 402 c4a_* symbols of the
    chemometrics4all 1.9.0 ABI, plus an idiomatic tier-2 R API for 15
    operators commonly used in NIRS chemometrics: SNV, MSC, EMSC,
    SavitzkyGolay, FirstDerivative, SecondDerivative, ToAbsorbance,
    KubelkaMunk, Detrend, AsLS, AirPLS, KennardStone, SPXY, YOutlierFilter,
    and WaveletDenoise. The bindings produce bit-equivalent results to
    libc4a within the 1e-6 binding-parity tolerance (Gate 1).
License: CECILL-2.1
URL: https://github.com/chemometrics4all/chemometrics4all
BugReports: https://github.com/chemometrics4all/chemometrics4all/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Suggests:
    jsonlite,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: libc4a (chemometrics4all C ABI) >= 1.9.0
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
NeedsCompilation: yes
